:qa -> close all panes at once
:wqa -> save and close all panes at once
:sp -> split horiz
:vsp -> split vertically
f12 see buffers
in normal mode: s-1 and s-2 -> to swicth between buffers



nnoremap     <Leader>R : %s/
nnoremap     <Leader>r : .,$s/
nnoremap     <Leader>c :bd<CR>
nnoremap     <F5> :ls<CR>:b
nnoremap     <Leader>u :noh<CR>
nnoremap     <F8> :diffupdate<CR>
nnoremap     <F6> :diffthis<CR>
nnoremap     <F7> :diffoff<CR>
"comment-uncomment
vnoremap <Leader>9 :norm i#<CR>
vnoremap <Leader>8 :norm ^x<CR>

" toggle easily paste mode
nnoremap <silent><Leader>0:set invpaste paste?<CR>
set pastetoggle=<Leader>0
set showmode

" Buffers - explore/next/previous: Alt-F12, F12, Shift-F12.
nnoremap <silent> <F12> :BufExplorer<CR>
nnoremap <silent> ! :bp<CR>
nnoremap <silent> @ :bn<CR>
nnoremap <silent> <Leader>1 :bp<CR>
nnoremap <silent> <Leader>2 :bn<CR>

s-a : go end of line and insert
,-s : save
''  : go last location in file
,-0 : paste mode
,-r : replace
,-q : buffer prec
,-w : buffer next
,-9 : comment
,-8 : uncomment
,-c : kill the buffer
,-h : highlight line
,-g : unhighlight

